<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_5c2728f6-3ca3-4f18-bf26-efdac9fbbb7c" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><sptc>E2F2</sptc><title id="_735fda1d-9778-453e-a7bb-daa8707286ed">Functional statement 2</title><archive-num>2019: GF2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_f1fd93a5-532a-4c34-8b5d-a5a88792ea34" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9405f9f5-fc9b-43b2-a7a4-5e9921ec58c1">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A heating, cooling and/or ventilation system must support energy efficient outcomes and minimise any impact on building occupants of adjoining spaces, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_5417bc48-0382-4d21-ba72-2676fd8e9901" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator's</xref> infrastructure, property and environment.</p></subclause></clause>